     FTARI      UP   E           K DISK
      *
     C                   IF        TATANR = X_TATANR AND TADATO = X_TADATO
     C                   IF        TADTS <> 0
     C                   DELETE    TARIR
     C                   ELSE
     C                   UPDATE    TARIR
     C                   END
     C                   ELSE
     C                   MOVE      TATANR        X_TATANR          8 0
     C                   MOVE      TADATO        X_TADATO          8 0
     C                   UPDATE    TARIR
     C                   END
      *
